BlogspotImporter
================

This tool will parse your Blogspot export xml file.


Example
=======

@blog = BlogspotImporter::Blogspot.import("#{RAILS_ROOT}/public/blog-03-04-2011.xml")

@blog looks like this:

[ 0 => {  title   => 'title'
          content => 'content'
          tags    => [tag1, tag2, tag3]
       },
  1 => {  title   => 'title'
          content => 'content'
          tags    => [tag1, tag2, tag3]
       },
]

